    <!--
        Bold download icon — safe zone 18..90.
        Parts:
          1. Arrow  — shaft (x 46–62, y 12–48) + chevron head (30,44)→(54,68)→(78,44)
          2. Tray   — U-shape: sides (x 18–28 & 80–90) + base bar (y 78–86)
          3. Link   — two small pills at the bottom to suggest a URL chain
    -->

    <!-- 1 · Download arrow (shaft + chevron, single filled path) -->
